\c 15
\s IJerusalema injengevini elingelazithelo
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 2 Ndodana yomuntu, isihlahla sevini siyini ngaphezu kwaso sonke isihlahla, \add kumbe\add* ugatsha oluphakathi kwezihlahla zegusu\x + 8.17.\x*?
\v 3 Kuzathathwa kiso isigodo yini ukwenza umsebenzi? Bangathatha kiso isikhonkwane yini ukuthi balengise lasiphi isitsha kiso\x + Isa. 22.23.\x*?
\v 4 Khangela\x + Joha. 15.6. Heb. 6.8.\x*, siyanikelwa emlilweni sibe yikudla, umlilo uqede izihloko zaso zombili, lokuphakathi kwaso kutshiswe. Siselosizo kuwo umsebenzi\x + 2 Kho. 19.10.\x* yini?
\v 5 Khangela, lapho sisaphelele, asenziwanga sibe ngumsebenzi; kuncane kangakanani lapho umlilo ususiqedile sesitshile sisezakwenziwa sibe ngumsebenzi\x + Jobe 9.14. 15.16. Jobe 4.19.\x*!
\p
\v 6 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Njengesihlahla sevini phakathi kwezihlahla zegusu, engisinikele emlilweni sibe yikudla, ngokunjalo ngizanikela abahlali beJerusalema\x + 17.6. 19.10-14. Hlab. 80.8.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba ngizamisa ubuso bami bumelane labo\x + 14.8.\x*; bazaphuma ko\add munye\add* umlilo kuthi \add omunye\add* umlilo ubaqede\x + 2 Kho. 25.9.\x*; njalo lizakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 6.7.\x*, sengimise ubuso bami bamelana labo\x + 14.8.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo ngizakwenza ilizwe libe lunxiwa, ngoba benze isiphambeko, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 14.16.\x*.